this ends with him losing.

01:04.586 --> 01:05.891
So, you know,you can choose

01:05.935 --> 01:08.155
to let us go right now
and secure your future,

01:08.198 --> 01:09.373
or...

01:09.417 --> 01:11.071
wait and see what happens.

01:11.114 --> 01:13.812
