So, I was invitedto give the keynote speech

06:11.588 --> 06:14.374
at a 30 Under 30ATL Entrepreneurs banquet.

06:14.417 --> 06:16.201
Well, congratulations.
You should probably

06:16.245 --> 06:17.420
start working on that,
'cause I got to get to...

